## 1. Entity-Relationship (ER) / Class Diagram ‚Äî Database Schema

Generate a **class diagram** representing these MySQL tables, their columns, data types, and relationships:

### Tables & Columns

| Table | Columns |
|-------|---------|
| **department** | `department_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `department_code` (VARCHAR, UNIQUE), `department_name` (VARCHAR, UNIQUE) |
| **teachers** | `teacher_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `first_name`, `last_name`, `email` (UNIQUE), `password` (hashed), `role` (ENUM: 'admin','faculty'), `primary_phone`, `alternate_phone` (nullable), `department_id` (FK ‚Üí department), `designation` |
| **students** | `student_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `first_name`, `middle_name` (nullable), `last_name`, `DOB` (DATE, nullable), `email` (UNIQUE), `password` (hashed), `primary_phone`, `alternate_phone` (nullable), `department_id` (FK ‚Üí department), `year` (1-4), `semester` (1-8), `academic_year`, `status` (ENUM: 'active','dc','graduated') |
| **courses** | `course_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `course_code` (UNIQUE), `course_name`, `department_id` (FK ‚Üí department), `year`, `semester`, `teacher_id` (FK ‚Üí teachers) |
| **enrollments** | `enrollment_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `student_id` (FK ‚Üí students), `course_id` (FK ‚Üí courses, ON DELETE CASCADE), `academic_year` |
| **timetable** | `timetable_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `department_id` (FK ‚Üí department), `semester`, `day` (ENUM: Mon-Sat), `slot_id` (FK ‚Üí time_slots), `course_id` (FK ‚Üí courses) |
| **time_slots** | `slot_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `start_time` (TIME, UNIQUE), `end_time` (TIME) |
| **attendance_sessions** | `session_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `course_id` (FK ‚Üí courses), `session_date` (DATE), `created_by` (FK ‚Üí teachers), `academic_year`, UNIQUE(course_id, session_date) |
| **attendance_records** | `record_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `session_id` (FK ‚Üí attendance_sessions), `student_id` (FK ‚Üí students), `status` (ENUM: 'present','absent') |
| **student_fees** | `fee_id` (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `student_id` (FK ‚Üí students), `academic_year`, `total_fee` (DECIMAL), `paid_amount` (DECIMAL, DEFAULT 0) |
| **refresh_tokens** | [id](file:///C:/Desktop/frontend/app/src/context/AuthContext.tsx#19-143) (PK, INT, AUTO_INCREMENT), `user_id`, `user_type` (ENUM: 'student','faculty'), `role`, `token` (TEXT), `expires_at` (DATETIME) |

### Relationships (Cardinality)

- **department** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **teachers** (has many)
- **department** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **students** (has many)
- **department** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **courses** (has many)
