- **students** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **enrollments** (enrolled in many)
- **courses** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **enrollments** (has many enrollments)
- **courses** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **timetable** (scheduled in many slots)
- **courses** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **attendance_sessions** (has many sessions)
- **time_slots** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **timetable** (used by many entries)
- **attendance_sessions** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **attendance_records** (has many records)
- **students** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **attendance_records** (has many records)
- **students** 1 ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ * **student_fees** (has many fee records)

