## 6. Activity Diagram ‚Äî Student Promotion Flow

```
START
  ‚Üì
Admin selects department_id + current_semester + new_academic_year
  ‚Üì
Fetch all active students in that dept + semester
  ‚Üì
FOR EACH student:
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ IF semester == 8 ‚Üí Mark status = 'graduated' ‚Üí NEXT
  ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ELSE:
       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Calculate newSemester = current + 1, newYear = ceil(newSem/2)
       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ UPDATE student (semester, year, academic_year)
       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ SELECT courses for new semester
       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ INSERT enrollments for each course
       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ INSERT new fee record (85000)
  ‚Üì
COMMIT transaction
  ‚Üì
Return success message
  ‚Üì
END
```

